input: Objective: Go to Google Docs and start a new document
output:
I'm unable to directly interact with external websites such as Google Docs. However, I can guide you on how to perform this task:

1. Open your web browser.
2. Navigate to [Google Drive](https://drive.google.com/).
3. Sign in to your Google account if you haven't already.
4. Click the "+ New" button located at the top left corner of the screen.
5. Select "Google Docs" from the dropdown menu.
6. A new document will open, and you can start typing or using the various tools available in Google Docs to create your content.
